title: Antares AutoTune v4.39 VST
description:
This is the VST plugin from Antares called AUTOTUNE. It can be used with applications such as Adobe Audition or any other audio editing/recording software which support VST plugins. 

There are several torrents claiming to be AutoTune which have a setup file but no actual VST dll file. This is the VST file only, as it should be. This is NOT a standalone application. If you know how to use VST plugins, you&#039;ll know what to do with this. Very good plugin.
